cs.AI, cs.IOT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.DC 

The paper discusses the use of Artificial Intelligence (AI) in the context of Internet of Things (IoT), which suggests that it could belong to multiple sub-categories. The most likely sub-categories are cs.AI and cs.IOT, as the paper focuses on the challenges and solutions related to AI in IoT. The sub-categories cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) are also possible, as the paper discusses the technical challenges and requirements related to the deployment and management of AI in IoT networks.
